trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when a name conflict occurs while a strongly typed <xref href="System.Data.DataSet"></xref> is being generated.
trans-unit.target: Unntaket oppstod når det oppstår en navnekonflikt under forespørselsparameter av sterk type <xref href="System.Data.DataSet"> </xref> genereres.

trans-unit.source: The TypedDataSetGeneratorException class indicates that a conflict occurred while an attempt is being made to generate a typed dataset class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TypedDataSetGeneratorException indikerer at det oppstod en konflikt når det blir forsøkt å generere en typeangitt datasettet-klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor, or `null` if the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
